Package it.polimi.ingsw.model

Class EntryPatternGoal

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.model.EntryPatternGoal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class EntryPatternGoal extends Object implements Serializable
This class was designed to represent a single TileType entry in a "pattern" for a PersonalGoal card. Its usage was then extended to retrieve cards in a bookshelf that satisfies a CommonGoal
Since:
02/05/2023
Version:
2.0
Author:
Tommaso Trabacchin, Melanie Tonarelli, Emanuele Valsecchi, Adem Shehi
